001package edu.cnm.deepdive.codebreaker.model;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.time.Instant;
006import java.util.Date;
007
008public class Guess {
009
010  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
011  private final String id;
012
013  @SerializedName("text")
014  @Expose
015  private final String content;
016
017  @SerializedName("exactMatches")
018  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
019  private final int correct;
020
021  @SerializedName("nearMatches")
022  @Expose(serialize = false,deserialize = true)
023  private final int close;
024
025  @SerializedName("created")
026  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
027  private final Date timestamp;
028
029  Guess(String content) {
030    this.content = content;
031    id = null;
032    correct = 0;
033    close = 0;
034    timestamp = null;
035  }
036
037  public String getId() {
038    return id;
039  }
040
041  public String getContent() {
042    return content;
043  }
044
045  public int getCorrect() {
046    return correct;
047  }
048
049  public int getClose() {
050    return close;
051  }
052
053  public Date getTimestamp() {
054    return timestamp;
055  }
056}
